name: Tans
content:
Tans was a Ubese bounty hunter during the Imperial Era. They were a member of the crew led by Boushh that consisted of fellow Ubese who had been exiled from Uba IV, with Tans having been the most recently exiled.
Tans appeared in War of the Bounty Hunters – Boushh 1, a one-shot issue of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters comic book crossover event, which was written by Alyssa Wong with art by David Baldeón. After the release of the issue, Wong confirmed and shared further details from her script notes on her Twitter account, including Tans' non-binary gender and observations about their personality.
